{"type": "article", "id": 14781, "title": "Super Gangster", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-11T07:11:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000600ce1JjHqnNZiP4xSB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国潮牌 Palace Skateboards 推出了 Super Gangster 系列，以 Penny Loafers 这种经典的便鞋为原型，采用高档皮革制作，非常惹眼。 Palace Skateboards 一年来多次与 Adidas 合作来推广滑板文化，但这款皮鞋显然与画风不符，不知算不算是 Palace 扩大涵盖范围的信号。这款鞋有四种颜色，<a href=\"http://shop.palaceskateboards.com/collections/footwear\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142232oBI2WOk4R5781taH.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142233gcVlUSGn1EF8NCXz.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422331yI6c9VsBjTdnrZE.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}